name: UCommonSession_HostSessionRequest
doc: A request object that stores the parameters used when hosting a gameplay session

OnlineMode: Indicates if the session is a full online session or a different type
bUseLobbies: True if this request should create a player-hosted lobbies if available
ModeNameForAdvertisement: String used during matchmaking to specify what type of game mode this is
MapID: The map that will be loaded at the start of gameplay, this needs to be a valid Primary Asset top-level map
ExtraArgs: Extra arguments passed as URL options to the game
MaxPlayerCount: Maximum players allowed per gameplay session
